data.description:
Welcome home to Park Lake! This charming residence has everything you desire, starting with 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths. The spacious great room has high ceilings and a cozy fireplace, creating an inviting atmosphere for relaxation.  The large eat-in kitchen features an island with a breakfast bar, perfect for casual dining and entertaining. The primary bedroom is generously sized and includes a lovely bathroom with a garden tub, separate shower, double split vanities and a walk-in closet for added convenience.
Additional features of this home include a mother-in-law floor plan providing added privacy, a media closet for wireless internet, two-inch blinds throughout, new interior paint and flooring and a two car garage. This is truly a wonderful place to call home!
